full_desc: ADCID must match the ADCID of the center uploading the data
Only one Initial Visit Packet (PACKET="I", "IF", "IL") and Initial UDSv4 Visit Packet (PACKET="I4) is allowed per participant
The FTLD module VISITNUM must match the UDS VISITNUM from the same visit date
The LBD module VISITNUM must match the UDS VISITNUM from the same visit date
A UDS Packet must be uploaded before a Milestone Form
Two packets cannot have the same visit number (VISITNUM) if they are from different dates (VISITDATE)
Two packets cannot have the same visit date(VISITDATE) if they are from different visit numbers (VISITNUM)
Visit number (VISITNUM) for Follow-Up Visit Packets must be greater than Visit number (VISITNUM) for Initial Visit Packet or Initial UDSv4 Packet (PACKET="I" or PACKET="I4")
Visit number (VISITNUM) for UDSv4 Initial Visit Packets (PACKET="I4") must be greater than Visit number (VISITNUM) for of the last UDSv3 Visit Packet
Follow-Up Packet (PACKET="F") visit date (VISITDATE) cannot be equal to or from a date before the Initial Visit Packet or Initial UDSv4 Packet (PACKET="I" or PACKET="I4")
Follow-Up Packet (PACKET="FF") visit date (VISITDATE) cannot be equal to or from a date before the Initial Visit Packet (PACKET="IF")
Follow-Up Packet (PACKET="FL") visit date (VISITDATE) cannot be equal to or from a date before the Initial Visit Packet (PACKET="IL")

If submitting an Initial UDSv4 Visit Packet (PACKET="I4"), that participant must have an existing  Initial Visit Packet (PACKET="I") or Follow-Up Visit Packet (PACKET="F") from a visit date (VISITDATE) before the Initial UDSv4 Visit Packet
Some fields in the input record do not match with the submitted version
Provided PACKET code is not in the list of accepted packets for this module
Provided FORMVER is not in the list of accepted versions for this module
PTID must be an alpha numeric code that is no more than 10 digits
MODULE is not in list of accepted modules
Follow-Up visit cannot be submitted without an existing Initial Visit Packet
More than one IVP packet found for the participant/module
